@bfc2012

Your first time here? Well, let me say welcome to TPB. Anyway, they're saying "waiting for 1080 version" because they are basically reminding YIFY that his/her fans are anticipating their 1080 release... as they usually always does both resolutions. Is it pointless? Maybe. There is no guarantee that YIFY would have released a 1080 version, but at least they know it's wanted. That clear things up for you?

I will also be waiting for the 1080 version, as i'm downloading one right now that's 13GB, i will probably stop that one as i see YIFY will most likely release theirs soon. :)

Holy Mother of God! What a day this's been!! First I come across YIFY's rip of The Hobbit & then Life of Pi... my patience has paid off, finally... YIFY does Django Unchained & I'm all set... 

@Muddicks: There comes a time in an uploader's career when his rips no longer need ratings.

@EvilCorporateWhore: Dude, I like your username & your replies to bfc2012. Hardly have I seen people tackling trolls sans profanities... way to go!!
